OL,3,COver 100 jobs at risk as BT announce
OL,4,Cproposed Londonderry office closure
OL,6,FThe proposed closure of BT's office in
OL,7,FLondonderry would be "devastating" for
OL,8,Fthe city, the MP for the area has said.
OL,10,FColum Eastwood was speaking after the
OL,11,Ftelecoms company announced a
OL,12,Fconsultation with the Derry workforce
OL,13,Fon a closure plan.
OL,15,FFoyle MP Mr Eastwood said 140 jobs
OL,16,Fwere at risk.
OL,18,FBT has said some workers will be given
OL,19,Fthe opportunity to relocate to its
OL,20,Fmain Northern Ireland operation, at
OL,21,FRiverside Tower in Belfast city centre.
