OL,6,FIt is understood BT considers the
OL,7,FDerry office premises no longer fit
OL,8,Ffor purpose.
OL,10,F"This is devastating news for BT
OL,11,Fworkers, their families and the
OL,12,Fbroader local economy in Derry," said
OL,13,FSDLP representative Mr Eastwood.
OL,15,F"At a time when we need to be
OL,16,Finvesting more in jobs and
OL,17,Fopportunities in our city, the
OL,18,Fproposed loss of these jobs will have
OL,19,Fa serious impact.
