OL,6,F"I am in touch with senior leaders at
OL,7,FBT about these plans and am relaying
OL,8,Fthe outrage in Derry that staff and
OL,9,Fthe whole community will be feeling.
OL,11,F"Relocating these roles to India and
OL,12,FBelfast is a mistake, it makes
OL,13,Fregional economic imbalances worse and
OL,14,Fit's a direct transfer of opportunity
OL,15,Ffrom our city to other places that do
OL,16,Fnot need it.
