OL,6,F"I will be raising this matter
OL,7,Fdirectly with ministers in London and
OL,8,FBelfast. Both have indicated their
OL,9,Fcommitment to addressing the
OL,10,Fopportunity gap and it's time that
OL,11,Fthey put their money where their mouth
OL,12,Fis."
