OL,7,Fto the workers affected by this
OL,8,Fdecision.
OL,10,F"At a time when the north west is
OL,11,Fgrowing as an exciting place to live,
OL,12,Fwork and study in, BT's announcement
OL,13,Fflies in the face of the economic
OL,14,Fconsensus which is to create regional
OL,15,Fbalance.
OL,17,F"Most importantly, it is a hugely
OL,18,Fconcerning announcement for workers
OL,19,Fand their families."
