OL,6,FIn a statement, a BT Group
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "BT is going
OL,8,Fthrough an ambitious modernisation
OL,9,Fprogramme and consolidating buildings
OL,10,Fwithin its estate from more than 300
OL,11,Fto closer to 30, modern workspaces.
OL,13,F"We are considering closing our office
OL,14,Fin Derry-Londonderry and we are
OL,15,Fconsulting with colleagues and their
OL,16,Funions on our proposals.
